Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is one of Kid's announcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and rack your brains,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you modern-day Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:47.01,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Kid, Conan, and the Ryoma Treasure Illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:47.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid the Phantom Thief announced that he'll \Nreturn Ryoma's treasures at 8:00 pm tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:50.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Already, over a hundred people are \Ngathered outside the Suzuki Museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:55.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,hoping to catch a glimpse of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:02:01.77,Signs,,0,60,11,,{\a7}Suzuki Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:57.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! I wanna go there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:02:01.77,Signs,,150,0,0,,{\a9}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NKid                                                               Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget about it. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:01.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I agree. Stay away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:03.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For you to be worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I never said I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, it's a chance to see the genuine \NKid the Phantom Thief in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.78,Signs,,0,60,11,,{\fad(0,800)}{\a7}Suzuki Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will Kid really show up tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why is Kid, a phantom thief, \Ngoing to return stolen treasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And why is he going to do it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Space reserved for Kid the Phantom Thief \Nto return treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The mystery just keeps getting deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It really is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But if he's going so far out of \Nhis way to return what he stole,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:33.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,maybe it means he regrets the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way that villain \Nfeels a shred of remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch that bastard \Nfor sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:45.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And why does it have to be tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At first, he just said it would be "soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then he suddenly announced \Nit'd be tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The reason, Aoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is that it's going to rain tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He was waiting for the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:02.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you really come up with \Nthat yourself, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what my instincts as criminal police say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:11.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So Kid was waiting for the rain \Nbefore setting the day and time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:16.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It looks like it could rain any minute now,\N and tomorrow's forecast calls for rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So why does it have to be a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:26.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Well, maybe it has to do with the \N"washing" he mentioned in the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:31.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or maybe because it's easier to blend in\N with with an umbrella and raincoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:35.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So it was just a gut feeling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No! That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:41.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, {\i1}boy,{\i0} a crimefighting \Npro like me knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So it did come from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:50.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if Kid would base the date \Nand time of a crime on something so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I pointed that out, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And there's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Kid would do this \N{\i1}just{\i0} to return the treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:07.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tarumi, the exhibition sponsor, \Nand Hanamura, the appraiser, had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They suspect Kid will make it look \Nlike he's returning the treasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:15.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,only to steal Ryoma's gun belt, \Nthe main attraction of the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:20.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If it's such a pain, you should just \Nhave them cancel the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:23.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That Tarumi guy is strongly \Nopposed to the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:32.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When it means Kid could steal the \Nmost important treasure of the bunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't that weird behavior for a sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:41.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Especially since their exhibits have apparently\N been plundered by thieves several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. So Tarumi and Hanamura are disciples
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,of that Gozu guy who tried \Nto kill me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:55.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I hope you'll finally be able \Nto catch him this time, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got a gas mask prepared just in case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:03.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and we've decided on a code word \Nthat'll trip Kid up if he's in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:08.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We even installed metal detectors,\N since Kid will be carrying that pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be celebrating by this time tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:15.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the precious \Ninfo as always, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:20.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I still wonder what he meant \Nby "washing" in his notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:24.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's probably just a play on Ryoma's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think Kid the Phantom Thief \Nis that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:37.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think a pro thief would go to all \Nthe trouble just to return stuff, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My guess is that \Nhe's got some other purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Another purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:48.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rain... washing... \NMaybe they're hinting at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not Kid, so what do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please step through the gates one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next person, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:04.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:05.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?! I should be able \Nto wear what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Creep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look anything like the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:23.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the first place, Kid would never \Njust stroll through the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't be too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I'm not that fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let the game begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:55.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,Space reserved for Kid the Phantom Thief \Nto return treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:55.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. They sure were polite \Nto reserve me a space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:58.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like the moniker goes, \NKid is a "phantom" magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:07:02.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,Space reserved for Kid the Phantom Thief \Nto return treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna follow your guidelines...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'll show up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:19.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Space reserved for Kid the Phantom \NThief to return treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:16.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A phantom thief wouldn't appear \Nwhere they tell him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:23.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn cosplayer. \NThinks this is a convention...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun, there's something that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:33.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't picture Kid, a thief, just coming \Nto return treasures that he stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I suspect he has some ulterior motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,An ulterior motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rain... washing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:47.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe those are major clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you really come up with \Nthat by yourself, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:08:00.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Little bastard... \NDon't tell me he's on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Phantom Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The length is 17 centimeters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so that's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,About this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:35.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,June 24th, 1867.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:39.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ryoma mentioned this pistol in a \Nletter to his older sister, Otome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"It's 17 centimeters and holds five bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:50.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's smaller than a dagger, but can \Nkill a man from 90 meters away."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:09:00.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How'd you smuggle that in? \NDid you go through the gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:04.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All I had to do was remove the lead \Nfrom the grip and waltz right through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's really light this way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:10.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Although lugging this many of them \Nwas a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:16.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you one thing. This time, I really \Ndid come just to return the stolen goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So don't get in my way, Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please don't push.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Ran-nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought you could get crushed \Nin this crowd, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Imagine what it'll be like \Nby the time Kid announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's something on your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:57.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It looks like writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Iron One"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:06.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of secret code?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:11.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say, did you bump into something \Nin the exhibit room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was pushed against the \Ncase of the gun belt exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on. Give me a \Nlittle more time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:27.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, I wonder how \NKid the Phantom Thief will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, it's something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He isn't our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Since he's an accomplice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You two look really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:43.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though Kid may be coming to \Nsteal your precious treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. And besides, he's not \Ncoming to steal treasures tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's coming to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's really it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What else would he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:05.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If he stole something, the police would \Nbe on him like that and it'd be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kid won't be the one \Nwho's arrested this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Take good care of that ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Handicraft Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who is that brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Little turd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's figured it out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll give your filthy natures
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a good washing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:33.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How's the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:38.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir! Nobody's turned around and left \Nwhen they saw the metal detectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are there any problems \Nat the metal detectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:44.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No. And no one's come through \Ncarrying that pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on in the \NRyoma exhibition room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At the moment, no one who \Nlooks like Kid is around,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but I wonder if he's even \Ngoing to show up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:58.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid has never announced an \Nappearance and then blown it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Five more minutes until \Nthe time he announced...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When the show starts, I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's just too bad that I won't \Nget to see the wonderful show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, ladies and gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:28.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It looks like Kid did have \Nanother motive, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:37.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid may show up any time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just an elementary school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll leave Kid to you police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't wanna get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:49.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get wet? What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:52.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there are too many people in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Security isn't worth a damn\N when it's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You look like my deceased husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid-sama, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's standing on the gun belt case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about, "washing"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:34.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll catch you and wash you to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the idea. But to wash \Nsomething, you need water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Observe as I make it rain in this one room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:14:00.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of a... He used fire \Nto activate the sprinklers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! I thought you were \Ngonna return those three items!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:11.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This shower will make everything clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just as rain washes away muddy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Can't see him with the steam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:23.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That villain! He must have tampered \Nwith the sprinkler's water pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:31.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The exit is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:41.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's very crowded, so please \Nproceed slowly towards the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Follow wet footprints \Nthat go through the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But there are wet footprints \Nall over the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why he waited for a rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:05.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then what about the three items \Nhe said he was gonna return?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He left them on top of the gun belt case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:12.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is no good. My blood got on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:17.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But it seems that all three were just \Nreplicas, so there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The problem is this gun belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The security system inside \Nthe case has been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:30.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the gun belt inside is a fake that \NKid switched out with the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The explanatory plaque on that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Something's dripping from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:52.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)}This gun belt was a fake all along. \NThey made a large quantity of them on \Nthe assumption that they would be stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He stuck a duplicate plaque with the same \Nmessage in watercolor paint over the original,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:57.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so when water hit it, the paint would run, \Nrevealing the secret message underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:01.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, Inspector. After \Nthe washing comes the drying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:05.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So put these two clowns out \Nto dry! I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:09.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see! My sleeve was wet \Nfrom the rain outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:13.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So the watercolor letters on the gun belt \Nexplanation plaque came off reversed on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:16.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So? What's this secret message underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:17.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"This gun belt was a fake all along..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:27.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They made a large quantity of them on the \Nassumption that they would be stolen. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:33.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The important part was that the thefts \Nmade news and got a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Ryoma Relics Stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:38.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So they mass-produced replicas \Nof the items beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:42.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and used third parties to sell them\N to wealthy Ryoma fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,who were all told they were getting the item\N that was stolen the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:50.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The beauty of this scheme is that even if \Nthe buyers realize later they bought a fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,they can't report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:58.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If they filed a complaint, they'd have to \Nadmit they secretly bought stolen merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:05.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why Phantom Lady's crime didn't come \Nto light after those three items were stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:10.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then she entrusted you with all \Nthe replicas she'd collected
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:14.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and asked you to expose \Nthose two con men, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:19.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The crime would need both an exhibition \Nsponsor who knew they were fakes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:24.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and a crooked appraiser who would claim \Nthose replicas were the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ryoma poseur phantom thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:36.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is the message on this plaque true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No! It's bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the first place, where is this \Nso-called "large quantity" of fakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All I see are this light \Npistol made out of plastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a counterfeit sake cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and a phony letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:55.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I just noticed I'm wearing \Nthis gun belt with the pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:01.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A card on the belt says, "Borrowed \Nfrom Tarumi-shi's warehouse"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:06.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Blast you, Kid! He used the crowd \Nto slap belts around all our waists!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:12.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You sabotaged the security system yourself \Nto make it look like the belt was stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and then afterwards sold copies of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:23.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This exhibit also has a plaque with a \Nmessage under the washed-away paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.16,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,The materials used are new and the method of \Nproduction is modern, so in conclusion, this\N hanging scroll can't be from the Bakumatsu period.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Pull," it says...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He wants me to pull on this scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ryoma's letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And they're all multiple \Ncopies of the same one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:46.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They look exactly the same as the \None left on the gun belt case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's a setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:56.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's no proof that \Nwe made and sold these forgeries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just did what Kid's plaque said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,The materials used are new and the method of \Nproduction is modern, so in conclusion, this\N vase can't be from the Bakumatsu period.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Crush."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:09.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey. There's a ton of sake cups inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It looks like each one \Nof them has blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:19.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If we run a DNA test on the blood, it will \Nbecome obvious who fabricated these cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will you lie like before and say you \Ntouched them all with a wounded finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You wiped your own blood \Non all of these cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:32.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure we'll find plenty of evidence\N when we search your warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:36.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Probably a mountain of unsold fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:39.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you figured out I was Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I look like a middle-aged guy\N you'd see anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:48.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even fake plastic pistols take up a lot \Nof space if you carry them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And even more so if you've also got \Na bunch of letters and sake cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So I looked for somebody in the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:59.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,who had an especially slim lower half \Ncompared to the rest of their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:04.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I found you, pretending to be fat so \Nyou could hide all those replicas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:08.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And of course, you're in disguise, \Nso there's no sweat to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:14.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So I stuck this button-sized transmitter \Nsticker to your skinny ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:20.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I located your position with my tracking \Nglasses and called out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:26.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So? Are you gonna turn me over\N to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This time I'll let you go, \Nout of deference to Ryoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you a Ryoma fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She once played Ryoma's big sister, Otome, \Nand fell madly in love with Ryoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:47.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But the reviews called her too cute to play \NOtome, which turned out to be a career boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:52.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, it sounds like we're \Nboth no match for our moms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is Phantom Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:11.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks to me getting the runs, I was holed up \Nin the museum bathroom the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And you stayed with me, so you didn't get \Nto see Kid the Phantom Thief, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:21.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's okay. Anyway, he's probably just some \Nmiddle-aged fat guy who looks like a thug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not that fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can say that now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:45.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Be sure to follow the adventures of \Nthat pint-sized great detective, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That means it's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:28.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I intended to spend a quiet \NChristmas Eve at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but Aoko's gonna have a party and \Nwants me to help her with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:34.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And what's this? Kid has sent out \Nanother advance notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It sure as hell wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wanna take a break that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:41.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:43.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,Holy Night: Two Kid the Phantom Thieves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Night: Two Kid the Phantom Thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:46.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
